\"part\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 264}, {\"ngram\": \"the global \\\"Shiny Claims, Dirty Flames\\\" campaign\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 316}, {\"ngram\": \"the Fair Steel Coalition\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"Green Advocates International\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"the harmful effects\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By Franklin Doloquee, contributing writer Holding aloft the symbolic torch emitting black smoke, the community members conveyed the devastating impact on their livelihoods, health, and natural resources.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Franklin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7497307390896783e-21, \"text\": \"Franklin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Franklin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Franklin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"writer Holding\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"the symbolic torch\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"black smoke\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"the community members\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"the devastating impact\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"their livelihoods\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 665}, {\"ngram\": \"health\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"natural resources\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The torch served as a powerful emblem of their grievances and the irony of the situation-a symbol of Olympic ideals turned dark by the realities they face.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The torch\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful emblem\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"their grievances\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"the irony\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"a symbol\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic ideals\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"the realities\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr. Sam Yeadieh, a community leader from Grand Bassa, delivered an impassioned speech on behalf of the affected communities, articulating the deep-seated frustration and dissatisfaction that has festered over the years.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 1075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999960629989084, \"rank\": 3.920135529122645e-06, \"text\": \"Sam\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a community leader\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Bassa\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"an impassioned speech\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the affected communities\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"the deep-seated frustration\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"dissatisfaction\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We present warm greetings to our local leaders, lawmakers, the government of Liberia, and the management of ArcelorMittal Liberia,\\\" Mr. Yeadieh began.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1484236317264604e-14, \"text\": \"Liberia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberia\"}, {\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ArcelorMittal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\"}, {\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1484236317264604e-14, \"text\": \"Liberia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"warm greetings\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"our local leaders\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1124}, {\"ngram\": \"lawmakers\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"the management\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr. Yeadieh\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We stand here as aggrieved communities from Nimba, Bong, and Grand Bassa Counties to express our profound dissatisfaction with the operations of ArcelorMittal in our regions.\\\"\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nimba_County\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.125327033311863e-16, \"text\": \"Nimba\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nimba_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nimba_County\"}, {\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Bassa_County\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grand Bassa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Bassa_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Bassa_County\"}, {\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ArcelorMittal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"aggrieved communities\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"Bong\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"our profound dissatisfaction\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"the operations\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"our regions\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued, \\\"We present to you a torch with black smoke, symbolizing the dark reality we face due to your operations in our communities.\\\"\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"black smoke\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"the dark reality\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"your operations\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"our communities\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr. Yeadieh detailed the myriad ways in which ArcelorMittal's activities have upended their lives.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ArcelorMittal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr. Yeadieh\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"the myriad ways\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1584}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today marks the first time we have united as affected communities to voice our collective frustration over the impact of ArcelorMittal Liberia's work in our areas.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ArcelorMittal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\"}, {\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1484236317264604e-14, \"text\": \"Liberia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Today\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"affected communities\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"our collective frustration\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"our areas\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, this significant day arrives during a very dark period in our lives.\\\"\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this significant day\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"a very dark period\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"our lives\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He described how lands have been seized, livelihoods destroyed, and homes damaged by vibrations from mining blasts and heavy machinery.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lands\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"livelihoods\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"homes\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1971}, {\"ngram\": \"vibrations\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"mining blasts\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy machinery\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pollution of air and water, coupled with the constant noise from blasting and trains, has left residents in a perpetual state of distress.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pollution\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"air\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"the constant noise\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"blasting\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"trains\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"a perpetual state\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"distress\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite their proximity to ArcelorMittal's operations, these communities suffer from inadequate healthcare, poor sanitation, and a lack of economic opportunities.\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ArcelorMittal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ArcelorMittal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their proximity\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"these communities\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"inadequate healthcare\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"poor sanitation\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"economic opportunities\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our living conditions have deteriorated due to the destruction of our farmland, medicinal resources, and protein sources, without adequate compensation or prior information,\\\" Mr. Yeadieh emphasized.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our living conditions\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"the destruction\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"our farmland, medicinal resources\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"adequate compensation\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"prior information\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr. Yeadieh\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On this dark day, we declare that we are not satisfied.\\\"\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this dark day\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Echoing his sentiments, Evelyn Saye and Abel Nyanamah of Nimba County highlighted the damage to their homes and farmlands caused by blasting, the pollution of rivers and streams used for drinking, unresolved grievances, and the exclusion of communities from decisions regarding the County Development Fund.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Evelyn\", \"score\": 0.9999999521392067, \"rank\": 4.661960882130929e-08, \"text\": \"Evelyn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Evelyn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Evelyn\"}, {\"begin\": 2657, \"end\": 2662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nimba_County\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.125327033311863e-16, \"text\": \"Nimba\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nimba_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nimba_County\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his sentiments\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"Abel Nyanamah\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2653}, {\"ngram\": \"the damage\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"farmlands\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"blasting\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"the pollution\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"rivers\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2765}, {\"ngram\": \"streams\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"drinking\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"unresolved grievances\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2818}, {\"ngram\": \"the exclusion\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"the County Development Fund\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also spoke of the harassment and criminalization of community members by state forces, further exacerbating their plight.\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 3033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the harassment\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"criminalization\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"community members\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"state forces\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"their plight\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dada Konkah of Nimba County asserted, \\\"We are not criminals; we are indigenous people who depend on the land and forest for our sustenance.\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3035, \"end\": 3039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0764575259508766e-18, \"text\": \"Dada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dada\"}, {\"begin\": 3050, \"end\": 3055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nimba_County\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.125327033311863e-16, \"text\": \"Nimba\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nimba_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nimba_County\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"criminals\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3094}, {\"ngram\": \"indigenous people\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"the land\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"fores